data.description: Discover the ideal home in the coveted Wicklow neighborhood, positioned right off Belfast River Road. This four-bedroom features a bonus room and three full baths. The main level provides convenient single-story spacious living, boasting three bedrooms, two full baths, stylish LVP flooring, and newer carpeting. The screened porch offers views of a peaceful backyard, enhanced with trees and a picturesque lake. Upstairs you'll find ample storage, a walk-in attic, additional bedroom, and a versatile flex space with a full bath. Built by SeaCoast builders, this home includes custom trim throughout, sprayed foam insulation, custom cabinetry, a meticulously finished garage, two hot water heaters, hardi cement board, and a brick exterior. Wicklow's prime location offers proximity to the Bryan County Complex, schools, sports facilities, Coastal Georgia waterways, and an effortless commute to Savannah, beaches, and I95. This one is a must see!
